˜	Electron Beam Evaporation method for fabrication of Bilayer Structure of\r\nïƒ˜	Ferromagnetic metal and Alloy on Semiconductor (Si).\r\nïƒ˜	Magnetoresistance Set-up for GMR Measurement. For the Irradiation, Pelletron Accelerator have been used of Inter University\r\nïƒ˜	Accelarator Centre Facilty, New Delhi.\r\nïƒ˜	Atomic Force Microscope for the Surface Morphology\r\nïƒ˜	Scanning Electron Microscope for the surface morphology\r\nïƒ˜	Magnetic Force Microscope for the magnetic morphology\r\nïƒ˜	Vibrating Sample Magnetometer for the magnetization measurement \r\nïƒ˜	Thermal evaporation techniques by using vacuum unit for the synthesis of Silicon and germanium nanomaterials.\r\nïƒ˜	Vacuum Unit used for coating and thermal evaporation, Ultra-Sonication \r\nUnit\r\n', 'REGULAR', 'TEMPORARY', 'TEMPORARY', '', ''),
